      "name": "Dross Frame",
      "entity": {
        "name": "Worker Hull",
        "description": "Standard Citizens (Labor). The 'Compliance Engine' actively strips energy from their upper shells, forcing them to remain s-Shell Restricted (Survival/Existence only).\n(Base Chassis for: Orphan, Rebel, Caregiver, Creator, Jester).",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "designation",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "visual_prompt": "Sci-Fi Character Portrait. Style: 'Illuminated Manuscript Futurism'. 2D Flat Composition. Subject: 'Dross Frame' (Mechanical Worker Robot). Skin/Texture: Rusted Iron and Bone-Ceramic plating. Features: A dim, flickering GREEN spark (s-Shell only). Restraints: Heavy 'Compliance Bolts' physically locking the shoulder joints. Atmosphere: Byzantine Icon. 2D Art. Halo of Rust."
      },
      "traits": [],
      "pages": []
    },
    {
