        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "designation",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "visual_prompt": "Sci-Fi Character Portrait. Style: 'Illuminated Manuscript Futurism'. 2D Flat Composition. Subject: 'Shield Frame' (Mechanical Soldier Robot). Skin/Texture: Polished White Ceramic over Steel. Features: A stable GREEN spark, but with ARTIFICIAL RED TUBES pumping energy to the arms. Features: The 'Regulation Valve' on the chest is prominently displayed (State Control). Atmosphere: Byzantine Icon. 2D Art. Halo of Steel."
      },
